---
// src/components/WebhostingHero.astro
---

<section class="relative bg-[#0f0f0f] text-white py-12 md:py-16 lg:py-20">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 lg:gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Linker kolom: tekst + knoppen -->
      <div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <div class="flex">
            <iconify-icon icon="mdi:star" class="text-yellow-400 text-lg" />
            <iconify-icon icon="mdi:star" class="text-yellow-400 text-lg" />
            <iconify-icon icon="mdi:star" class="text-yellow-400 text-lg" />
            <iconify-icon icon="mdi:star" class="text-yellow-400 text-lg" />
            <iconify-icon icon="mdi:star-half-full" class="text-yellow-400 text-lg" />
          </div>
          <span class="text-sm font-medium">4.9/5 – 1737+ beoordelingen</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight mb-5">
          Een <span class="text-primary">razendsnelle</span><br>
          website, <span class="text-primary">zonder gedoe</span>.
        </h1>

        <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-8 max-w-xl">
          Laat het zware werk aan ons over. Wij verhuizen je site <strong>gratis</strong> of zetten je nieuwe website direct online op onze premium servers. Alles geregeld.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 mb-8">
          <a
            href="#pakketten"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-primary text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-semibold text-base hover:bg-primary-dark transition shadow-lg"
          >
            Bekijk pakketten ↓
          </a>
          <a
            href="/verhuisservice"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center border-2 border-primary text-primary px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-semibold text-base hover:bg-primary/10 transition"
          >
            Gratis verhuisservice
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-300">
          <iconify-icon icon="mdi:shield-check" class="text-green-500 text-xl" />
          <span>30 dagen risicoloos proberen</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Rechter kolom: alleen de afbeelding -->
      <div class="hidden lg:block relative">
        <img
          src="/images/webhosting.jpg"
          alt="Razendsnelle webhosting bij GetHost"
          class="w-full rounded-2xl shadow-2xl object-cover"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>